# Steering File Rules

- Keep shared rules in agent-agnostic files: `AGENTS.md`, `PRODUCT.md`, `TECH.md`, `STRUCTURE.md`, `VISION.md`, and `DESIGN.md`.
- Keep tool-specific syntax and workflow hints in the tool-specific files.
- Preserve exact steering file names and capitalization.
- Keep instructions short, concrete, and tied to this repository.
- Update related steering files when repo conventions change.
- Do not copy long vendor documentation into this repo; summarize and link instead.
